text: Supercell is a company that makes free games. Their games include Hay Day (2012), Clash of Clans (2012) Boom Beach (2014), Clash Royale (2016), Brawl Stars (2017) and Squad Busters (2024). Their games run on smart phones and tablets with Android or iOS.
